{
  "stem": "26609.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They just took away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was very hard to obtain food, very hard, food to obtain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to stand in-- in the long queues, or we had children or no children, we still had to stand for-- for days in queues to get a little bit of, I think a few grams of sugar or bread or anything.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Food was very hard to obtain, unless-- it was called-- on the black market, it was called [NON-ENGLISH], who had money and could get it privately, you know, aside.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, it was on-- we had to wait in long queues for-- for bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, nothing particular.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was something else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who was not-- you see, the Germans came from the other side, because I think Lodz was already occupied in [INAUDIBLE] by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came to other-- to our side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we still had-- were under the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We thought the Russians were here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the people fled from the-- before the Germans came in, fled from the other side of Poland, from the west.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in the east.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lwow is in east Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fled to-- to our side, to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You've heard of it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] They fled from their places-- Refugees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--where the Germans were already occupied, because west Poland was earlier occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came from Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And east was still and the Russians came from the other side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they fled from there to our place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't know that the-- the Russians are here, the communists.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Russians didn't want them, so they-- oh, it was awful.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
